<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA61">
<l>aṉṟun tiruvuruvaṅ kāṇātē yāṭpaṭṭē</l>
<l>ṉiṉṟun tiruvuruvaṅ kāṇkilē - ṉeṉṟuntā</l>
<l>ṉevvuruvō ṉumpirā ṉeṉpārkaṭ keṉṉuraikkē</l>
<l>ṉevvuruvō niṉṉuruva mētu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without seeing the sacred form that day I have become a servant</l>
<l>and today I cannot see the sacred form [either]. Any day,</l>
<l>what will I tell those who ask “the lord is one of which form?”</l>
<l>Which form? Which is your form?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
